From da42f03da4d45f7df0eeb75bb7a613dbf529d164 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: mrtn au <s-mauer@ucp.pt>
Date: Sat, 18 Jul 2026 23:29:46 -0400
Subject: [PATCH] Merge interview studio + real Maschmeyer data into the
 vetting suite
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Replaces the fictional dummy pipeline with the real Maschmeyer Group
opportunity DB (Secfix, deskbird, VoiceLine, Timefold, Climatiq, Pliant)
from public sources, plus one fictional Acme demo card. Real founders are
never scored — 'not assessed' is enforced through the data model.

Ports Laura's live interview studio into React:
- /interviews: scripted live call, real-time vibe-check meters, and a
  'super negotiation' ZOPA model with interactive levers + deal-fit score.
- /founder: 5-axis psychogram (Recharts radar), team overlay with a gated
  complementarity score, collapsible live-evidence quotes, and a guardrail
  banner. Wired the routes into the sidebar nav.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 <noreply@anthropic.com>
